    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 25</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You hypnotize yourself, becoming convinced you are completely invincible and indestructible, standing up to any enemy, fearless and confident. You gain a +6 morale bonus to Will saves against feat effects, and a +2 morale bonus to attack and weapon damage rolls, De- fense and skill checks.</p>\n\n\n\n",
